INSTALL NOTES

When install is done go to:
Preferences -> Plugin
Add: Label, Extractor
Click OK 

Open preferences again
->Extractor
Change path to /mnt/downloads/torrent
Tick off "Create torrent name sub-folder"
Deluge is now set up
